extends ./layout
block content

  header(role='banner')
    .content
      nav.cf
        h3.pull-left LevelDB
        ul.unstyled.pull-right
          li
            a(href='https://github.com/rvagg/node-levelup/blob/master/README.md', title='Docs') Docs
          li
            a(href='http://hereishow.to/@leveldb', title='Examples') Examples
            span.label Soon
          li
            a(href='https://github.com/level', title='See LevelDB organization on Github') Github

  .content
    section.intro
      h1 Level Databases
      h3 Level DataBases offer a single, cross platform interface with a multitude of back-ends optimized for different use cases.
      a(href='https://github.com/level', class='button button-primary button-large', title='View on Github') View on Github

    section.conferences
      h3 Conference Talks

      .column
        h4 Upcoming Talks

        dl
          dt: a(href='http://campjs.com/#leveldb') LevelDB (workshop)
          dd <a href='https://twitter.com/hij1nx'>Paolo Fragomeni</a> at <a href='http://campjs.com/'>CampJS</a> (May 23&ndash;26th 2014)

        dl
          dt LevelDB (sessions and workshops)
          dd Various camp counsellors at <a href='http://nodeconf.com/'>NodeConf</a> (July 3rd&ndash;6th)

        dl
          dt: a(href='http://forwardjs.com/training-sessions/#goto-303') LevelDB + Node.js: A persistance renaissance (workshop)
          dd <a href='https://twitter.com/hij1nx'>Paolo Fragomeni</a> at <a href='http://forwardjs.com/'>Forward.js</a> (July 24th 2014)

      .column
        h4 Past Talks

        dl
          dt: a(href='http://nodejsconfit.levelgraph.io/') How to Cook a Graph Database in a Night
          dd <a href='https://twitter.com/matteocollina'>Matteo Collina</a> at JSConf.it (2014)

        dl
          dt: a(href='http://r.va.gg/presentations/nodeconfeu.2013/') A Real Database Rethink
          dd <a href='https://twitter.com/rvagg'>Rod Vagg</a> at NodeConf.eu (2013)

        dl
          dt: a(href='https://www.youtube.com/embed/4_22ie--Rzs') A modular database?
          dd <a href='https://twitter.com/dominictarr'>Dominic Tarr</a> at NodeConf.eu (2013)

        dl
          dt: a(href='https://www.youtube.com/embed/41oDDTRWjIQ') Level me up, Scotty!
          dd <a href='https://twitter.com/juliangruber'>Julian Gruber</a> at NodeConf.eu (2013)


